                                        <h2 class="highlight highlight-primary highlight-bg-opacity highlight-animated mb-2" data-appear-animation="highlight-animated-start" data-appear-animation-delay="300" data-plugin-options="{'flagClassOnly': true}">เมนูของเรา</h2>
                                    </div>
                                    <p><strong class="font-weight-bold text-3 positive-ls-2 mb-3 ms-2 text-dark">FROM OUR FARM TO YOUR TABLE.</strong></p>
                                    <div class="py-0  mb-3">
                                        <p class="text-color-dark text-4 line-height-8  mb-0">
                                            <p>Ohkaju Vegetable Garden We select the best ingredients to create menus. that are delicious for the health of customers, including salads and steaks, served with fresh organic salad vegetables Delivered straight from our garden every morning. Passed cleaning with the ozone system. Customers can be confident in every dish because we choose the best for them.</p>
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="testimonial-author d-block ">
                                        <a href="https://www.ohkajhu.com/เมนู" class=" font-weight-medium text-3 btn-px-5 py-3">
